{
  "message": "fix(patterns): broaden Gemini usage warning regex and add corpus fixtures\n\n- patterns.rs: expand usage warning regex to match alternative phrasings\n  (\"approaching your usage limit\", \"usage limit approaching\") alongside\n  the existing \"Usage limit warning/approaching\" prefix.\n- Add Gemini test corpus fixtures: model_used_alt, session_resume_hint,\n  session_summary_tokens, and usage_warning with expected detection JSON.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
